{"tid":2090432,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緬甸一個翡翠礦區山泥傾瀉　至少50人死亡","createTime":"2020-07-02T07:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T08:09:32.000Z","uid":1002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1bbb633062169ed4cfbe1a9d8e92cd7f4f1bc5","tid":2090432,"uid":1002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535384-20200702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535384-20200702.htm&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8PY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=cee8a6e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535384-20200702.htm&h=2bafe723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535384-20200702.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸一個翡翠礦區發生山泥傾瀉，至少50人遇難。<br />\n<br />\n事發於北部城鎮帕敢一個翡翠礦區，當地早上時間6時許，工人採礦期間被暴雨後引發的山泥掩埋。報道說，大約有200人被困。消防部門在社交網站表示，搜救工作仍在進行，目前發現至少50名遇難者遺體。"},{"pid":"6ac7aa960a064f95b02f074370b4bea285c57e55","tid":2090432,"uid":1002,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/國安法通過-古巴-緬甸-埃及等-53-國表態支持-港區國安法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%B4-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8-%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%E7%AD%89-53-%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8PY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=d58b0925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E5%8F%A4%E5%B7%B4-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8-%E5%9F%83%E5%8F%8A%E7%AD%89-53-%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%85%8B%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%2F&h=99a49770\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/